<title>USA: Loehmann files for 1.97 mln shr offering.</title>
<headline>Loehmann files for 1.97 mln shr offering.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-09-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Loehmann's Inc said on Friday it has filed a registration statement with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission to the offering of 1.97 million shares by selling shareholders.</p>
<p>Montgomery Securities will lead manage the offering and Robertson Stephens &amp; Co and Salomon Brothers will co-manage the offering.</p>
<p>Certain selling shareholders have granted the underwriters a 30-day option to buy up to 295,500 shares to cover overallotments, Loehmann's said.</p>
